68
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,880
Tapos na ba tayo sa mga costume?

69
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:21,960
Oo, kami nga.

70
00:06:21,961 --> 00:06:23,120
Kung gayon, tara na.

71
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,000
Tara na.

72
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:32,560
Kung malaki ang pagkakamali mo, gagawa ka ng paraan para ayusin ito.

73
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,040
Salamat po, ginoo.

74
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,480
Pagod ka na ba?

75
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,760
Hindi.

76
00:06:55,080 --> 00:06:57,160
Wala naman talagang ibang gagawin ngayon.

77
00:06:58,200 --> 00:06:59,200
Malaya kang umalis.

78
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,960
Ayos lang 'yan.

79
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:05,000
Mananatili ako hanggang dulo at
iuuwi kita pagkatapos.

80
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,880
Hindi pa ako sigurado.

81
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,720
Baka doon ako tumuloy sa bahay ng tatay ko.

82
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,720
Sige.

83
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,280
Uy, uy.

84
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:18,640
