108
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,560
Hindi na ako mahilig diyan.

109
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:42,760
Pasensya na. Maghanap ka na lang ng playlist ng iba.

110
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,480
