00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,520
Magpatawad.

173
00:14:57,560 --> 00:14:58,560
Magpatawad.

174
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,840
Magpatawad.

175
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:00,920
Magpatawad.

176
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:01,800
Magpatawad.

177
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:03,040
Magpatawad.

178
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:05,160
Magpatawad.

179
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:05,920
Patawad.
Aba?

