219
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,200
Tumigil ka. Pinapahiya mo ako.

220
00:19:21,080 --> 00:19:22,959
Nandito na ang delivery.
Kukuha ako ng kape.

221
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:23,960
Oo.

222
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,880
Naku, Jack.

223
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,560
Ganun na ba ka-stress ang trabaho ko sa'yo?

224
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,920
Umiinom ka na.

225
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:42,480
Hindi. Naramdaman ko lang.

226
00:19:48,393 --> 00:19:50,073
Uy, nasaan si Dean?

227
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:51,880
Hindi ko siya nakita ngayon.

228
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:00,680
Hindi ko alam.

229
00:20:01,280 --> 00:20:02,720
Naghiwalay na kami, kaya wala akong pakialam.

230
00:20:04,800 --> 00:20:07,160
Uy, pasensya na.

231
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,000
